docs {
  # Get All Institutes

  Retrieves a paginated list of all institutes in the system.

  ## Query Parameters
  - `limit` (optional): Number of results to return (default: 10)
  - `offset` (optional): Number of results to skip (default: 0)

  ## Response
  Returns an array of institutes with pagination metadata including total count.
}
